</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_124" id="61v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Herman von Preytenstein, lantrichter czu
                        Aurbach</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her lantrichter, uns hat fürgelegt Hans Süszell,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz Herman Kesell dem Friczen Kessell,
                                    <add><expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan></add>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, seine <add>erbe an
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan></add> gute czu Ermreich, <add>das hinter
                            dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger gelegen sey</add>, für ew auf das
                        lantgeriht gen Awrbach geladen hab und er im doch des
                            <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> czu helffen nye
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan> hab. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> klager daran weisen wollet, daz
                        er von der klag lasz, das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> derselb <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan>
                        Kesell czu des <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> icht
                                <expan>czusprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darümb so wil im derselb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan> slewnigs
                            <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er des
                                <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan> wirdt. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii post <expan>Urba<ex>n</ex>i</expan>.</ab>
</div>
